reviewText: Good transfer quality for both movies.  Excellent price too!
Have always loved both of these movies.  Great entertainment!!!
For a used DVD there is no problems with these movies.  Visable there was some scratches but I haven't found a skip in the DVD so far.  I will know better when I watch the whole movie.
I loved this movie. And I love that I can now watch it whenever I want to. I even had my granddaughters watch it with me one day. We had movie night and we all sat and laughed and cried together.
The movies where enjoyable to watch even though I had seen them before, but the price was very good to put into the library.  Woul recomment this product
